| ApprovedAt | DateTime? | Thời điểm duyệt |
| UserId | Guid | Index, no FK |

### PostStatus enum

```text
Draft          = 1
Queued         = 2
Generating     = 3
Ready          = 4
Scheduled      = 5
Publishing     = 6
Published      = 7
Failed         = 8
Cancelled      = 9
WaitingReview  = 10   // Chờ duyệt
Approved       = 11   // Đã duyệt, sẵn sàng lên lịch/đăng
GeneratingMedia = 12  // Đang sinh ảnh AI
NeedMedia       = 13  // Thiếu media sau khi image gen hết retry
RenderingTemplate = 14 // Đang render overlay template
NeedFix           = 15 // Render overlay hết retry
```

### Workflow transitions

```text
Draft/Ready → submit-review → WaitingReview
WaitingReview → approve → Approved
WaitingReview → reject → Draft
Approved → schedule → Scheduled (+ PublishJob Pending)
Scheduled → cancel-schedule → Approved
Approved/Scheduled → publish-now → Publishing (+ PublishJob Pending)
```

### GenerationFlow enum

```text
FullAI = 1   // Luồng 1: sinh text + image song song
RAG    = 2   // Luồng 2: sinh text → vector search media
```

