## GenerationJobs — Queue xử lý song song + retry

| Cột | Kiểu | Ghi chú |
|---|---|---|
| Id | Guid (PK) | + BaseEntity |
| PostId | Guid | Index, no FK |
| JobType | int | JobType enum |
| Status | int | JobStatus enum |
| FlowType | int | GenerationFlow enum (FullAI/RAG/Fallback) |
| Priority | int | Default 0 |
| RetryCount | int | |
| MaxRetries | int | Default 3 |
| IdempotencyKey | string(200)? | Index — tránh duplicate queue |
| ErrorCode | string(100)? | |
| ScheduledAt | DateTime? | Retry delay |
| StartedAt | DateTime? | |
| CompletedAt | DateTime? | |
| ErrorMessage | TEXT? | |
| InputPayload | TEXT? | JSON — prompt, params |
| OutputPayload | TEXT? | JSON — kết quả |

### JobType enum

```text
TextGeneration  = 1
ImageGeneration = 2
ImageOverlay    = 3   // Logo + CTA
MediaMatch      = 4   // RAG vector search
Publish         = 5
```

### JobStatus enum

```text
Pending    = 1
Processing = 2   // Running
Completed  = 3   // Succeeded
Failed     = 4
Retry      = 5   // Retrying
Cancelled  = 6
DeadLetter = 7   // Hết retry
```

### Text generation mock pipeline

```text
Draft/Queued/Failed → queue-text-generation → Queued (+ job Pending)
Queued → process → Generating → WaitingReview (+ job Completed)
Pending/Retry → fail → Failed/DeadLetter (+ Post Failed/Queued)
Failed/DeadLetter → retry → Retry (+ Post Queued)
Pending/Retry/Processing → cancel → Cancelled (+ Post Draft)
```

### Image generation mock pipeline

```text
WaitingReview/NeedMedia/Failed (+ có Content) → queue-image-generation → GeneratingMedia (+ job Pending)
GeneratingMedia → process → GeneratingMedia → WaitingReview (+ MediaAsset + PostMedia Cover)
Pending/Retry → fail (còn retry) → Failed (+ Post WaitingReview)
Pending/Retry/Processing → fail (hết retry) → DeadLetter (+ Post NeedMedia)
Failed/DeadLetter → retry → Retry (+ Post GeneratingMedia)
Pending/Retry/Processing → cancel → Cancelled (+ Post WaitingReview)
```

### Image overlay/render pipeline (ImageOverlay job type)

```text
WaitingReview/NeedFix/Failed (+ Content + PostMedia) → queue-image-render → RenderingTemplate
RenderingTemplate → process → WaitingReview (+ MediaAsset Overlay + PostMedia Cover replaced)
Pending/Retry → fail (còn retry) → Failed (+ Post WaitingReview)
Pending/Retry/Processing → fail (hết retry) → DeadLetter (+ Post NeedFix)
Failed/DeadLetter → retry → Retry (+ Post RenderingTemplate)
Pending/Retry/Processing → cancel → Cancelled (+ Post WaitingReview)
```

Render: ImageSharp overlay (headline + CTA bar) → `rendered/yyyy/MM/dd/{guid}.png`, fallback copy nếu lỗi.

