## PublishLogs — Lịch sử publish + retry tracking

| Cột | Kiểu | Ghi chú |
|---|---|---|
| Id | Guid (PK) | + BaseEntity |
| PostId | Guid | Index, no FK |
| SocialChannelId | Guid | Index, no FK |
| AttemptNumber | int | 1, 2, 3... |
| Status | int | PublishStatus enum |
| ExternalPostId | string(500)? | ID trên platform |
| PublishedUrl | string(1000)? | URL mock/thật trên platform |
| RequestPayload | TEXT? | Sanitized |
| ResponsePayload | TEXT? | Sanitized |
| ErrorCode | string(100)? | |
| ErrorMessage | TEXT? | |
| PublishedAt | DateTime? | |
| IdempotencyKey | string(200)? | Index — publish:{postId}:{channelId}:{scheduledAt} |

### Scheduler config (appsettings)

```json
"Scheduler": {
  "Enabled": true,
  "IntervalSeconds": 30,
  "BatchSize": 10
}
```

`ScheduledPostPublisherService` quét post `Scheduled` với `ScheduledPublishAt <= UtcNow`, gọi `IPublishPipelineService.ProcessDueScheduledAsync`.

Manual trigger: `POST /api/publishlog/process-due` (Admin/ContentManager).

### Publish mock pipeline

```text
Pending     = 0
Success     = 1
Failed      = 2
RateLimited = 3
Cancelled   = 4
Processing  = 5
DeadLetter  = 6
```

### Publish mock pipeline

```text
Approved/Scheduled → publish-now/schedule → Publishing (+ PublishLog Pending + GenerationJob Publish Pending)
Pending → process → Processing → Success (+ Post Published)
Pending/Processing → fail → Failed/DeadLetter (+ Post Approved/Failed)
Failed/DeadLetter/RateLimited → retry → Pending (+ Post Publishing)
Pending/Processing → cancel → Cancelled (+ Post Approved/Scheduled)
Idempotency: không publish lại nếu Post.ExternalPostId hoặc PublishLog Success đã tồn tại
```

